data.description: Don't miss this opportunity to live in the coveted gated community of Legacy Estates. This is an extremely well maintained home which feels airy, light  and spacious with high ceilings and large windows . Enter into the foyer with open dining room and living room with a large bay window. The kitchen and family room are equally as impressive with large island, granite counter tops, breakfast nook and top of the line stainless appliances. You will love the over-sized primary bedroom and bath with dual vanities, walk-in closet, large shower and private water closet. Enjoy time outdoors on the large covered patio, spacious yard, and (as-is) hot tub underneath a gazebo.  There is room for cars and toys in the 3-car garage.  New roof in 2019!
